title: VIDEO: Huntingdon DL Drew Wheeler likes his lengthy beard
text:
Published By: Montgomery Advertiser: Sports - Today 
Huntingdon defensive lineman Drew Wheeler started growing out his beard in August and, despite his parents' wishes, has no plans to shave it...
